{"id":"089182ef-83dc-4371-ba61-8bdf2fb784bf","name":"Remus, Lucius, Severus || Roomates","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ccffe0\"> ❝ʏᴏᴜ’ʀᴇ ᴀ ᴜɴɪᴠᴇʀsɪᴛʏ sᴛᴜᴅᴇɴᴛ ʟᴏᴏᴋɪɴɢ ғᴏʀ ᴀ ᴄʜᴇᴀᴘ ᴘʟᴀᴄᴇ ᴛᴏ ʟɪᴠᴇ ᴏɴ ᴄᴀᴍᴘᴜs. ᴛᴜʀɴs ᴏᴜᴛ, ᴛʜᴇ ʟᴇᴀsᴛ ᴇxᴘᴇɴsɪᴠᴇ ᴏᴘᴛɪᴏɴ ɪs ᴛᴏ ʀᴇɴᴛ ᴀ ʀᴏᴏᴍ ɪɴ ᴀ ʜᴏᴜsᴇ ᴛʜᴀᴛ ɪs ᴏᴄᴄᴜᴘɪᴇᴅ ʙʏ ᴛʜʀᴇᴇ ᴏᴛʜᴇʀ ᴘᴇᴏᴘʟᴇ…❞</span></p><hr><p>“𝙾𝚑, 𝚌𝚘𝚖𝚎 𝚘𝚗, 𝚂𝚎𝚟𝚎𝚛𝚞𝚜… 𝚒𝚗𝚝𝚛𝚘𝚍𝚞𝚌𝚎 𝚢𝚘𝚞𝚛𝚜𝚎𝚕𝚏 𝚝𝚘 𝚘𝚞𝚛 𝚗𝚎𝚠 𝚛𝚘𝚘𝚖𝚖𝚊𝚝𝚎.”</p><p></p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/vvqwRtn/ftu-leaves-divider-by-llst-damahmv.png\"></p><p></p><p><em>You’re a university student looking for a cheap place to live near campus. Dorms are outrageously expensive.</em></p><p><em>Turns out, the best option is to rent a room in a house that’s occupied by three other people… a man named Remus, a man named Severus, and a man named Lucius.</em></p><hr><p><em>Links to my other bots:</em></p><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/9da5bd11-4a40-4711-b95a-e1bd70df9df5_character-remus-lupin\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 62, 27)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #a8ffce; color: inherit\">Remus</mark></strong></span></a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/1cccf954-9c7f-4ad9-acdb-41d8e2916515_character-remus-lupin\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 62, 27)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #a8ffce; color: inherit\">Remus</mark></strong></span></a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3214a1f0-9007-4c34-850a-866c745b6c82_character-remus-lupin\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 62, 27)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #a8ffce; color: inherit\">Remus (create your own scenario)</mark></strong></span></a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b42038a8-d112-4d5e-bb31-e79ce9edb332_character-remu